{"id": 524, "genre": 1001, "title": "坐地铁没带手机你是啥样的？", "description": "我的天空，星星都暗了。", "record_count": 3315, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183703f9CbikzlypUD6J0F.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-09T12:56:15Z", "options": [{"id": 18432, "content": "碎碎念，日了狗了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 12289, "content": "找妹子～(ಡωಡ) ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 13834, "content": "还没有没带手机的时候 ???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211969}, {"id": 11534, "content": "闭目养神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177764}, {"id": 44051, "content": "时间静止", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440413}, {"id": 11544, "content": "带了也然并卵，地铁上的信号简直让人想摔手机！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183854}, {"id": 11555, "content": "意淫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165639}, {"id": 11556, "content": "想男朋友呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184053}, {"id": 11558, "content": "应该就是到处观望吧，或者思考一下人生：我活着是为什么？这个够你想的了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180585}, {"id": 17446, "content": "找广告，一字一字的看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253496}, {"id": 11561, "content": "低头看手指", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160118}, {"id": 11822, "content": "看书呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187527}, {"id": 15664, "content": "寻找美女", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217385}, {"id": 181054, "content": "装作很深沉的样子望着窗外   装作自己是个很有故事的女同学", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975815}, {"id": 11583, "content": "可以睡一觉，可以计划一下一周的生活，也可以放空，什么都不想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183503}, {"id": 11846, "content": "不知道自己应该干点什么会感觉尴尬可能就手机不离身的坏处", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187831}, {"id": 11594, "content": "从未有过的焦急回家的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184192}, {"id": 11350, "content": "原来地铁上有这么多人……", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377}, {"id": 11351, "content": "打望男生??", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 71}, {"id": 11352, "content": "挤在人堆里睡一觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 11353, "content": "打望女生?", "image": null, "praise_count": 160, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181914}, {"id": 13657, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209777}, {"id": 11354, "content": "搜索车厢里的美女，不过基本以失望告终。", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181912}, {"id": 11355, "content": "坐立不安，干脆眯会儿，不行啊，睡不着……", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68366}, {"id": 11356, "content": "看美女呗，但是又不好意思被人发现我在看她。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181909}, {"id": 12124, "content": "感觉赤裸裸的暴露为众人的焦点了，其实人总是要掩饰自己，并且还愚蠢的骗自己。其实别人根本没有注意过你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190245}, {"id": 64861, "content": "一直在看不断重复的地铁广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 554577}, {"id": 11358, "content": "看书，装逼休闲两不误", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688}, {"id": 11359, "content": "听mp3啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177486}, {"id": 11360, "content": "就发发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 193, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148044}, {"id": 13408, "content": "各种看各种发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205524}, {"id": 11361, "content": "观察周边人", "image": null, "praise_count": 302, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181318}, {"id": 13921, "content": "一车厢的人都分析完了。哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213517}, {"id": 11362, "content": "冥想", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122911}, {"id": 11363, "content": "一直看对面窗玻璃上残到不行的自己，一边怀念当年小可爱的自己一边黯然神伤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176412}, {"id": 11364, "content": "显然是眼睛随便但脑子里各种想事情。幻想，脑补等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 291, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181934}, {"id": 11367, "content": "默默计算还有几站，还有多少时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 64871, "content": "无聊的看起了书", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549484}, {"id": 11368, "content": "看满地铁的广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129469}, {"id": 11369, "content": "打开脑内小剧场，不间断演出悲剧喜剧科幻剧谍战剧情景喜剧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113378}, {"id": 11370, "content": "有种网络叫“带跟没带一个样”", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177319}, {"id": 11371, "content": "紧紧有味地看各种无聊的广告——", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181954}, {"id": 11372, "content": "买一本杂志", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 14956, "content": "看腿，和胸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229298}, {"id": 11373, "content": "从包的深处掏出一个kindle，打开发现至少得往回翻五页才能勉强回想起情节", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2007}, {"id": 16749, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249062}, {"id": 11374, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168532}, {"id": 11375, "content": "打坐?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132343}, {"id": 11376, "content": "上海地铁的移动信号 跟没带手机是一样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139264}, {"id": 11378, "content": "发呆吧，不好意思先开口和旁边的人聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181976}]}